description:
© 1999, 2015 CWMPC all rights reserved.
Here is the RAW, CANDID  footage from camera masters of the day at the RockWalk when the guitar Greats were inducted. If you have never been able to get inside a RockWalk induction this is what it was like when Steve Vai, Jimmy Vaughan, Larry Carlton and Joe Satriani were inducted.. We decided to put up as much of the raw footage as we can so true fans could see the CANDID footage of these icons and a glimpse into the behind the scenes and see who shows up to honor these guitar hero's... Enjoy!!
